title: Posts not showing up
body: So i posted a couple threads on these boards but they were not posted, no one saw them no replies. not even sure if this one will be seen, if by some chance this post is seen what could be preventing posts from being posted?

replies.body: It's possible that you are not meeting the level requirement for the region of the board you are attempting to post in.  You can post here in H&S because there is no level minimum.  You may need to reach 15 or 20 depending on where you'd like to post.  Hope that helps!
I can see this post just so you know.
